author: @POOKIE4SKZ
text:
Dear Stray Kids,

I hope you’re all doing great! I wanted to let you know how much you mean to me. You’re my favorite group, and your music brings me so much joy and inspiration. Each song and performance is amazing, and you all inspire me every day. I dream of seeing you live one day, but right now, I can’t afford to attend your concerts. Even though I’m cheering for you from afar, I want you to know how much I support and love you. Your hard work and dedication are truly incredible. I have a couple of special requests. First, I would be thrilled if I could get a pined. It would make me so happy to have a little piece of your support. Second, if there’s a chance to be mentioned in one of your upcoming videos, even just a little mention, it would be a dream come true. It would mean so much to me to feel a bit closer to you. I also want to thank Woojin. Even though he’s no longer with the group, he will always have a special place in my heart. His voice and presence were wonderful, and I hope he’s doing well and finding happiness. By the way, I’m only 12. To Bang Chan, Lee Know, Changbin, Hyunjin, Han, Felix, Seungmin, I.N, and Woojin—thank you for everything. I’m so proud to be a Stay and will always support you no matter what
